                    </div>
                    <span>I just finished reading this wonderful, beautiful book and I had to sit down and share my feelings about it, so anyone thinking of reading this book won't wait.<BR>I won't go into the details of the story, since that is already done in the Amazon description. I will tell you that The Shadow of the Wind is one of the best books I have ever read. I read a lot of books, sometimes 2 to 3 a week, so when I say it is one of the best I have ever read, it is really saying something. I had already told someone they could borrow it when I was finished, now I am sitting here trying to figure out how to back out of that promise, I don't want it leaving my hands!!!<BR>So do what I did, read this book quickly because once you start, you will have no choice. Then go back and start over, read it slowly and enjoy the writing, the story and the total experience. Bravo Mr. Carlos Ruiz Zafon.</span>
                  
