                    <span>A book that seems like it was waiting for you since before you were born. A brilliant conception, masterfull execution, with a translation that is simply a blessing. Fermín is a character both from the ages and for the ages. <P>Certainly better than any book by Arturo Perez-Reverte, whose books I have enjoyed.</span>
                  
              
